# Configures EKF3 to use optical flow (HereFlow) as a velocity backup source (SRC2).
# GNSS remains the primary source (SRC1). An optical flow calibration flight is required
# before source switching will be accurate (see 64_optical_flow_results.param).
# FLOW_TYPE=6 (HereFlow) is already set in 15_general_configuration.param.
# All EK3_SRC* params not listed here are at firmware defaults and do not need to be set.
EK3_SRC2_VELXY,5  # Optical flow horizontal velocity for backup source. 5=OpticalFlow. Firmware default is 0 (disabled) — this is the only non-default change needed for optical flow backup.
